description: Action for the Development of Marshall Islands Renewable Energies (ADMIRE) Project MSP

subproject.description: This project will facilitate the following: (i) increased number of RE hardware installations on the ground which enhances productivity and income generation (ii) enhanced institutional capacity to coordinate, finance, design, supply and maintain RE installations (iii) improved accessibility of capital for RE businesses (iv) strengthened legal and regulatory instruments to support renewable energy dissemination, financing and marketing, and (v) improved awareness, skills and knowledge.
